> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港發生乜野事<br />\n<br />\n大把稅收, 盈餘下, <br />\n只要撥多d 錢落去MPF 對沖果度, 好快就成事<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">垃圾預算案, 搵個無能兼無腦會計佬去做財爺起劏房波</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">反而MPF 對沖<br />\n全民退保, 醫保<br />\n勞工假, 銀行假問題<br />\n立法5天工作制<br />\n最高工時<br />\n</span><br />\n呢d 實事, 隨時仲簡單又唔去做, 推都唔撚識推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2蚊乘車, 以前殖民地推既話, 點會由正苦比架<br />\n一定由港督由商界(太古 etc ) 帶頭自己做, <br />\n國泰工會點解咁強大, 都係當年前港英正苦要太古放權<br />\n<br />\n理財新哲學：無條件減利得稅, 免差餉<br />\n<br />\n長遠措施無樣野做到<br />\n有心攪樓市<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">租金管制</span>好應該推動出黎傾下啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n澳門都立法規定<br />\n強制性假日返工要「三工」<br />\n<br />\n香港法例仍然係講緊最少要比員工放勞工假咋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民就業<br />\n帶頭無條件減利得稅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8e3e00df36674cddc56612d6246bec0f7bc104b","tid":610812,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cefbcdf94b692f35557b37921702125bdc504f2","tid":610812,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T12:45:05.000Z","msg":"奴隸學人放假<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你傻架？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T12:46:16.000Z","msg":"slave多左5日吸取社會經驗，仲唔感謝"},{"pid":"7df0bebd6bda88e3cabb4698fd7cfd955437361a","tid":610812,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T14:41:43.000Z","msg":"反對"},{"pid":"c6ee4631b95b9660e6f943578c8ff00fd36e5624","tid":610812,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T00:46:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}